name: VAGINA DRY: VAGTASTIC VOYAGE
description:
Vagina Dry single(s) release tour!
Pōnoke !
Wellington !
First show of the north island line up at Valhalla with : Lavendermenace and No sector To celebrate our final single release: privileged man.
Doors open at 8pm | Presales $15

name: BARBARIANISM 5
description:
Barbarianism 5 Extreme Metal Fest The fifth gathering of NZ's darkest and heaviest extreme metal!
Three nights of the best Black/Death/Doom metal NZ has to offer!
One night at the fantastic Underworld tavern and two nights at our beloved mecca Valhalla!
Vendors with interesting and exciting stalls, awesome sets from carefully chosen bands of the highest calibre and the best crowd Wellington can gather!
A huge lineup this year, a titanic gathering of the best performing monster bands!

name: KLO-PROMOTION FUNDRAISER GIG
description:
Klo-Promotion presents the Klo-Promotion Fundraiser Gig, raising funds for Kloey Shaw's new event promotion business at university.
Join us on Thursday, July 31st at Valhalla.
Starring RENÉE, Jayme Morpeth, Jeline, and Bri Louise with Molly.
Doors open at 7pm Early birds: $5 + BF General admission: $10 + BF
